item.title: (317)RuneUnity - Just Released: Party Slayer with Cs, LS, Vorago, Teir 90 armour
item.dc:creator: @Loveandpower Loveandpower
item.description:
@Loveandpower wrote:

I (as normal lol) had my doubts for this server when I was starting to look for a new one. I was pleasantly surprised though these guys have a decent development team (I’ve been told they have several developers from R-S), and you see updates quite frequently.

This server also has some age on it and a lot of money has gone into the development of it.

The community is very healthy and there is a strong staff front where even the developers and admins have secondary accounts to play legit (just like how I used to in Myth-Scape!)

The economy seems to be well thought out as well. You won’t become rich over night and you won’t be able to be the best over night.
